name: DogeArmy
description: DogeArmy is a token built on binance smart chain. ($DOGRMY) is a Dogecoin reward token for DOGE fans. Our goal is to create a community where every doge fan can come together. We reward our holders through automatic $DOGE distribution for holding $DOGRMY. each transaction $DOGRMY holders will receive 7% in Dogecoin automatically distributed to their wallet. Just add the Binance-Peg Dogecoin Token contract address to your wallet and watch your rewards grow. DogeArmy had a fair launch: there was no public presale or private sale. LP tokens are locked for 3 years. DogeArmy is brought you by the Team that brought you Hummingbird Finance and NestSwap.
